title: MisterMusic Show 339 new indie,alternative,rock radio
description:
MisterMusic Show #339 (192 kbps stereo MP3) 120 minutes--



Several new tunes make their debut on the show this week from Sleater-Kinney, Man Without Country, and Mew. And another song from the latest album by Guster.
Plus we revisit 20 years ago to January and early February 1995, for a song that was number 1 on the modern rock chart for 7 weeks, in the 'Oldie of the Week' segment.

It's a blast of new indie and alternative music mixed with over 5 decades of hits- The MisterMusic Show.

Broadcasting weekly and heard on the web on Rock XS Radio internet radio.
